<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Chia Chen - i</ENAMEX> , senior executive vice president of the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Individual Banking Sector at Bank Sinopac</ENAMEX> -LRB- which <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">earlier this year</ENAMEX> created a stir in the industry by introducing the world 's <ENAMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">first</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">five</ENAMEX> - in - <ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">one</ENAMEX> money management account -RRB- has been observing the evolution of the financial environment in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Taiwan</ENAMEX> for <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">many years</ENAMEX> , and offers the following thoughts about trends in money management .
