<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Chiu Shean - bii</ENAMEX> of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">National Taiwan University</ENAMEX> was told in a recent meeting with the general manager of certain large <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">American</ENAMEX> commercial bank : " <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Asians</ENAMEX> always ask : ' Is the market going to go up or down <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">tomorrow</ENAMEX> ? '
